"2019-11-07T12:58:25.000Z","msg":"因為「國產」係笑話<br />\n而且我肯定啲技術偷完只會攞嚟發展軍事武器同支黨自用<br />\n垃圾國家"},{"pid":"493dc3922e73af002bbf362df6c2146dafc7aa6a","tid":1698322,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6e71db019ab0dfd7b0662fa11c5ffe99262a944","tid":1698322,"uid":40763,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T11:55:12.000Z","msg":"我都唔明點解要放生中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個國家冚國剷起哂佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:58:56.000Z","msg":"Trump 要連任 想利用5百億美元農業訂單 穩奪堆農業州 <br />\n習近平都覺得壓力大 經濟下行 物價通脹 黨內外壓力等<br />\n<br />\n暫時停戰 對雙方 都有好處<br />\n<br />\n但就好像佢地所講 第一階級協議是最早傾的野<br />\n之後果堆 根本唔會傾到 例如國企補貼"},{"pid":"fc62d283a5dc031c297e0c6e05ea3f960f6b3f1f","tid":1698322,"uid":283700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3157e17430590209740cd91e4b7e6d78ace0efa9","tid":1698322,"uid":120678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:18:44.000Z","msg":"點解生物醫藥領域中，支那偷左人地咁多技術但國產藥物仲係咁垃圾？<br />\n支那人生左cancer，要去搵印度平價仿製藥續命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:04:31.000Z","msg":"因為大數據睇病得既都步入中老年，唔死點養，如果有資產留比d仔女，9成入世未深，勇於創業同輸錢，d資金又入番市場 何樂而不為， 所以學番黎既生物醫藥一般都針對軍事，同上流社會人士。"},{"pid":"00dd3bb8c18b8028f6a9f4d52f8702f8d9ee0617","tid":1698322,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:21:14.000Z","msg":"咪撚歌收支那仔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}